title: UFC : events with the highest live attendance as of May 2019
summary: This is a bar chart. It shows Attendance for 18 number of Ufc Fightss.
The Attendance is appeared to be the highest at Ufc Fights Rousey vs Holm (UFC 193) and lowest at Ufc Fights Miocic vs Overeem (UFC 203).
The difference of Attendance between the highest and lowest Ufc Fights is 37429.0.
